    "description": "BanHown is a life simulation game in which assume the role of a person who must migrate to other provinces for subsistence farming, manage time and resources efficiently while immersing themselves in a Thai Ban style atmosphere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A variety of seeds can be purchased. Each store has its own unique items that can be bought and sold in different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/8294adbaebba2de39239756752c7d607.poster.avif?t=1769051990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/8294adbaebba2de39239756752c7d607.webm?t=1769051990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/8294adbaebba2de39239756752c7d607.mp4?t=1769051990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Players can plant seeds and take care of them by watering them until they mature. Once mature, the crops can be harvested and sold.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/51ab9097c06e2ab54e7a377346a308b8.poster.avif?t=1769051990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/51ab9097c06e2ab54e7a377346a308b8.webm?t=1769051990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/51ab9097c06e2ab54e7a377346a308b8.mp4?t=1769051990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Players can immerse themselves in the natural atmosphere and observe creatures according to weather conditions on the survey maps.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/50d337e8c266affda11bd547b28ca3d3.poster.avif?t=1769051990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/50d337e8c266affda11bd547b28ca3d3.webm?t=1769051990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269590/extras/50d337e8c266affda11bd547b28ca3d3.mp4?t=1769051990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Players can fish for leisure while waiting for crops to grow, either to sell for additional income or to find items in specific areas.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plan for future updates</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Add cooking feature<br></li><li>More types of vegetables that can be planted<br></li><li>Introduce a mission from a village NPC<br></li><li>More stories and NPC conversations<br></li><li>Add more equipment and facilities<br></li><li>Improve environmental details and introduce various buildings<br></li><li>Introduce dangerous animals in the area<br></li><li>Character's dexterity in the game</li></ul>",
